   <|"Data" -> ".md\nGreat! Now we know how to efficiently update all \
affected cells. The decay and flash functions are rather trivial to implement \
using a `Clip` and `Subtract` composition mapped over all elements:", 
    "Display" -> "codemirror", "Hash" -> 
     "6f816ef7-5b63-4bdb-a0b7-f94fbfd7e9a8", "Invisible" -> False, 
    "MetaOnly" -> False, "Props" -> <|"Hidden" -> True|>, 
