   <|"Data" -> "Great! Now we know how to efficiently update all affected \
cells. The decay and flash functions are rather trivial to implement using a \
`Clip` and `Subtract` composition mapped over all elements:", 
    "Display" -> "markdown", "Hash" -> 
     "f8bef09d-afa3-4a0f-9cce-75ba54661dfb", "Invisible" -> False, 
    "MetaOnly" -> False, "Props" -> <||>, "PublicFields" -> {"Properties"}, 
